"""validate quote special case for 1 value"""
quote = coins.get_quote_hitbtc([self.coin_list[0]])
assert isinstance(quote, pandas.DataFrame)
unique_values, unique_expected = helpers.find_uniques(list(quote.columns.
    values), self.expected_headers)
assert unique_expected == []
if unique_values:
    pytest.xfail('Unexpected values from get_quote_hitbtc(): {}'.format(
        unique_values))
assert len(quote) == 1
